    • 构造器详细资料

      • StringTable

        public StringTable(java.lang.String fileName,
           java.lang.String indexPrefix,
           int size,
           Metric metric)
            throws java.io.IOException
        The first line of the file should have two integers, separated by white space. The first is the dimension of the DoubleVector, the second is the total number of data points. Each following line is a DoubleVector, with each dimension separated by white space.
        参数:
        fileName - the filename of the source file
        size - number of data points to read
        抛出:
        java.io.IOException
